frames.caption: Two climbers in red gear are scaling a giant Coca-Cola bottle made of ice, set against a snowy mountain landscape. The scene is surreal, with the oversized bottle dominating the foreground while other climbers stand on the snow below. The bright sky and pristine snow create a striking contrast with the climbers' red outfits.
frames.description: The scene depicts a whimsical and imaginative setting where climbers are ascending a massive ice sculpture of a Coca-Cola bottle. The backdrop features snow-covered mountains under a clear blue sky, suggesting a high-altitude, cold environment.

frames.caption: In a surreal alpine landscape, climbers in red gear scale a gigantic Coca-Cola bottle made of ice. The scene captures the adventurous spirit as they ascend the icy surface with ropes and climbing equipment. The vast snowy mountains stretch into the horizon under a clear blue sky.
frames.description: The scene is set in a snowy mountainous region where climbers are engaged in an imaginative ascent of an enormous ice sculpture shaped like a Coca-Cola bottle. The juxtaposition of the climbers against the oversized bottle creates a whimsical and adventurous atmosphere.
